# AI Document Reader & Summarizer

Upload PDFs, extract text (OCR fallback), and generate summaries (abstractive/extractive).  
Features: Streamlit UI, TTS, export DOCX/PDF/TXT, user accounts.

ðŸ“„ AI Document Reader & Auto-Summarizer

An AI-powered application that reads PDF documents, auto-detects the document type, and generates optimized, context-aware summaries. Built using Python, Streamlit, NLP, and LLMs, this tool makes document understanding fast, intelligent, and user-friendly.

ðŸš€ Features

Auto-Detect Document Type
Automatically classifies uploaded PDFs into:

Research Paper
Notes
Assignment
Legal Document
Invoice
Medical Report
General Document

AI-Optimized Summaries
Generates smart summaries tailored specifically to the detected document type.

PDF Text Extraction
Extracts text from single or multi-page PDFs.

Clean Streamlit UI
Simple, modern interface for uploading documents and viewing summaries.

Lightweight & Fast
Works locally with minimal setup.

## Run locally
1. Install: `pip install -r requirements.txt`
2. Run: `streamlit run app.py`

## Notes
- Add `users.json` (excluded from git) or create accounts using the Register page.
- For OCR install: Tesseract and add to PATH.
